![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/011b4e87-15c4-4bf5-b9b0-1ec15e42c5a8/306.jpg)

Loki Season 2 is in the books and what a show it was! We laughed, we cried, and timelines died. Join us as we try our best to break down this incredible second outing, while also predicting the future (if any) of Loki in the MCU! We talk Loki but also the recent casting of The Sentry, talk the Madame Web trailer, and other rumors in the multiverse on this Thanksgiving episode of the Major Issues Podcast!  
  
Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

